      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and features a Bilstein suspension setup for optimized lateral kinematics. Finished in pristine Laguna Seca Blue with a flawless interior, this vehicle maintains strict mechanical and aesthetic integrity, free from typical E46 wear patterns. A turn-key performance icon for the technical purist.",
